records.name: Velassaru Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Velassaru, Velassaru Maldives is near the airport and on the beach. Maldives Islamic Centre is a notable landmark, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at Villingili Public Beach and Embudu Beach. Hulhumale Beach and Kurumba Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as windsurfing.
descriptions.general: Velassaru Maldives offers luxurious beachfront and over-water accommodation with uninterrupted ocean views. It features a wide range of water and adventure sports, as well as sunset cruises and yoga classes. Guests can enjoy relaxing spa treatments in over-water pavilions, or hop on a Maldivian boat and watch the crew demonstrate traditional fishing methods. Resort facilities include a fitness center, tennis court, and infinity pool with a view of the beach and the ocean. Chinese-speaking staff is available for assistance. Featuring wooden ceilings and floors for a tropical atmosphere, the bungalows and villas at Velassaru have air conditioning and ceiling fans. Each room is equipped with a flat-screen TV, international TV channels, and a DVD player. Some rooms also come with a Nespresso machine and wine chiller. The private bathroom comes with L'Occitane bath products, beach bags, and slippers.
